== Usage ==
This template is put at the top of a biographical article to explain to readers which part of a Korean person's name is the family name. If desired, the person's [[generation name]] can also be stated. The template will automatically link to the article (if one exists) of the specified family name. For example,

<code><nowiki>{{Korean name|Kim}}</nowiki></code>

will display

{{Korean name|Kim}}

If the family name article does not follow the "NAME (Korean surname)" naming convention, a link can be created manually, e.g.

<code><nowiki>{{Korean name|[[Won (surname)|Won]]}}</nowiki></code>

will display

{{Korean name|[[Won (surname)|Won]]}}

If the surname is stage or pen name, e.g.

<code><nowiki>{{Korean name|Lee|Han}}</nowiki></code>

will display

{{Korean name|Lee|Han}}

